{"title":"鼓浪行——秋游厦门鼓浪屿作","authors":["刘孚　王梦奎"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":10,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓浪行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——秋游厦门鼓浪屿作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘孚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久慕鼓浪屿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠悠南国情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上花园誉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遐迩素闻名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树深重阴绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花繁夹道红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来亦其时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋光正融融。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮头好风光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔白浪生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮升濯我足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮落濯我缨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目极海天界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椰阁何亭亭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低昂自在舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袅袅弄微风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽焉蔚蔚指顾处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼翠流丹下壁峰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞如瀑，彩如虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿若霞，繁若星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千枝万条匝重重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万紫斗千红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此花艳异伊阿谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国君子三角梅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以叶为花花非花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非花更比百花秾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乃知鼓浪之人眼不虚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍为市花著殊荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓浪风，鼓浪情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓浪风情何所钟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是公门私家俗相约，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喧喧车马绝无踪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全岛不见车马走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建国由初代相承。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有客四方至，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论尊与荣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安步以当车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"优游度从容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烦嚣远，尘埃净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天常蓝，气常清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安得如此净洁一方土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令人开怀吐纳滤心胸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将别鼓浪屿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮起难平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼望全球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生态忧忡忡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"污染至穷乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遑论邑与城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古来清风朗月不用一钱买，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今生存呼吸欲奔哪颗星！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣见三北林区起戈壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又闻沿海林带郁葱葱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上下四方齐努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四化环保同步行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何日廓宇内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州色色明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惠及草与木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泽被鱼和虫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再游鼓浪屿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶杖观太平。 　贺母校沁阳师范八十年校庆 　  　王梦奎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三朝兴废几沧桑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃李春风惠泽长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报国但凭三寸笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀师总系九回肠；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每从昨日思今日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却把他乡作故乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何当同为归去赋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三千弟子咏流觞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}